ğŸ¦ Simple Banking Program (Python)

This project is a beginner-friendly Python program that simulates basic banking operations.
Users can check their balance, deposit money, withdraw money, and exit the program.
It demonstrates core programming concepts such as functions, conditionals, loops, input handling, and validation.

âœ¨ Features
ğŸ’° Check Balance

View the current account balance at any time.

â• Deposit Money

Accepts positive deposit amounts

Rejects invalid inputs (negative values)

Returns the deposited amount which is added to the balance

â– Withdraw Money

Accepts withdrawal amounts

Ensures the withdrawal does not exceed the balance

Rejects negative inputs

Returns the withdrawn amount which is subtracted from the balance

ğŸ”„ Menu-Driven Interface

The user can choose from:

Show balance

Deposit money

Withdraw money

Exit the program

